      <ul class=\"necqa_notice__list\"> \r\n         <li class=\"necqa_notice__item\"> \r\n          <details class=\"necqa_notice__details\"> \r\n           <summary class=\"necqa_notice__summary\"> <span class=\"necqa_notice__summaryMain\"> <span class=\"necqa_notice__summaryText\"> 悪天候での配送遅延について </span> <span class=\"necqa_notice__icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span> </span> </summary> \r\n           <div class=\"necqa_notice__panel\"> \r\n            <div class=\"necqa_notice__panelInner\"> \r\n             <p class=\"necqa_notice__text\"> 悪天候や交通事情などの影響により、一部地域で配送に遅れが発生する場合があります。 最新の配送状況は各配送会社のお知らせをご確認ください。 </p> \r\n            </div> \r\n           </div> \r\n          </details> </li> \r\n        </ul> \r\n       </div> \r\n      </section> \r\n     </div> \r\n    </div> \r\n   </section> \r\n   <section class=\"necqa_categorySearch\" aria-labelledby=\"necqa-categorySearch-title\"> \r\n    <div class=\"necqa_categorySearch__inner\"> \r\n     <h2 id=\"necqa-categorySearch-title\" class=\"necqa_categorySearch__title\"> 項目から探す </h2> \r\n     <ul class=\"necqa_categorySearch__list\"> \r\n      <li class=\"necqa_categorySearch__item\"> <a class=\"necqa_categorySearch__link\" href=\"/navigate/direct/info/faq/product/index.html\"> <span class=\"necqa_categorySearch__icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"> <img src=\"//p4-nec.static.pub/fes/cms/2026/03/30/eovxk14ve2kn8pcpzi3xp7pjkkmomm299868.svg\" alt=\"\" width=\"64\" height=\"60\"> </span> <span class=\"necqa_categorySearch__text\">商品</span> </a> </li> \r\n      <li class=\"necqa_categorySearch__item\"> <a class=\"necqa_categorySearch__link\" href=\"/navigate/direct/info/faq/order/index.html\"> <span class=\"necqa_categorySearch__icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"> <img src=\"//p1-nec.static.pub/fes/cms/2026/03/30/ceptcsmmfe6pljp4nqfk88gst1zabt137326.svg\" alt=\"\" width=\"64\" height=\"60\"> </span> <span class=\"necqa_categorySearch__text\">ご注文・ご購入</span> </a> </li> \r\n      <li class=\"necqa_categorySearch__item\"> <a class=\"necqa_categorySearch__link\" href=\"/navigate/direct/info/faq/payment/index.html\"> <span class=\"necqa_categorySearch__icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"> <img src=\"//p3-nec.static.pub/fes/cms/2026/03/30/aef6hzzrl8b2stj0ahjcb90g51mmic888284.svg\" alt=\"\" width=\"64\" height=\"60\"> </span> <span class=\"necqa_categorySearch__text\">お支払方法</span> </a> </li> \r\n      <li class=\"necqa_categorySearch__item\"> <a class=\"necqa_categorySearch__link\" href=\"/navigate/direct/info/faq/login/index.html\"> <span class=\"necqa_categorySearch__icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"> <img src=\"//p4-nec.static.pub/fes/cms/2026/03/30/ju1jwhizcserw2yxoylank0syfy93n671870.svg\" alt=\"\" width=\"64\" height=\"60\"> </span> <span class=\"necqa_categorySearch__text\">お客様登録</span> </a> </li> \r\n      <li class=\"necqa_categorySearch__item\"> <a class=\"necqa_categorySearch__link\" href=\"/navigate/direct/info/faq/point/index.html\"> <span class=\"necqa_categorySearch__icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"> <img src=\"//p2-nec.static.pub/fes/cms/2026/03/30/pyc4g8bnpqzfm8gxx8vp7f69rmla5h146875.svg\" alt=\"\" width=\"64\" height=\"60\"> </span> <span class=\"necqa_categorySearch__text\">ポイントサービス</span> </a> </li> \r\n      <li class=\"necqa_categorySearch__item\"> <a class=\"necqa_categorySearch__link\" href=\"/navigate/direct/info/faq/pointmail/index.html\"> <span class=\"necqa_categorySearch__icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"> <img src=\"//p4-nec.static.pub/fes/cms/2026/03/30/m24kxytro8jptldj7qgonfcet3z13e384361.svg\" alt=\"\" width=\"64\" height=\"60\"> </span> <span class=\"necqa_categorySearch__text\">ポイントメール</span> </a> </li> \r\n     </ul> \r\n    </div> \r\n   </section> \r\n   <section class=\"necqa_faqContact\" aria-labelledby=\"necqa-faqContact-title\"> \r\n    <div class=\"necqa_faqContact__inner\"> \r\n     <h2 id=\"necqa-faqContact-title\" class=\"necqa_faqContact__title\"> お客様からよくいただくお問い合わせ </h2> \r\n     <ul class=\"necqa_faqContact__list\"> \r\n      <li class=\"necqa_faqContact__item\"> \r\n       <details class=\"necqa_faqContact__details\"> \r\n        <summary class=\"necqa_faqContact__summary\"> <span class=\"necqa_faqContact__summaryInner\"> <span class=\"necqa_faqContact__qMark\" aria-hidden=\"true\">Q</span> <span class=\"necqa_faqContact__question\"> 電話で問い合わせ／購入相談はできますか？ </span> <span class=\"necqa_faqContact__toggle\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span> </span> </summary> \r\n        <div class=\"necqa_faqContact__panel\"> \r\n         <div class=\"necqa_faqContact__panelInner\"> \r\n          <div class=\"necqa_faqContact__answerRow\"> \r\n           <span class=\"necqa_faqContact__aMark\" aria-hidden=\"true\">A</span> \r\n           <div class=\"necqa_faqContact__answer\"> \r\n            <p> NEC Direct（購入前のご相談・ご注文に関するお問い合わせ）は、お電話で承っておりません。 製品選び・購入手続きは「FAQ／チャット」をご利用ください。 ご注文後の確認（納期・注文内容・領収証など）は「マイページ」からご確認いただけます。 </p> \r\n           </div> \r\n          </div> \r\n         </div> \r\n        </div> \r\n       </details> </li> \r\n      <li class=\"necqa_faqContact__item\"> \r\n       <details class=\"necqa_faqContact__details\"> \r\n        <summary class=\"necqa_faqContact__summary\"> <span class=\"necqa_faqContact__summaryInner\"> <span class=\"necqa_faqContact__qMark\" aria-hidden=\"true\">Q</span> <span class=\"necqa_faqContact__question\"> 問い合わせ先はどこですか？（購入前／注文後／購入後） </span> <span class=\"necqa_faqContact__toggle\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span> </span> </summary> \r\n        <div class=\"necqa_faqContact__panel\"> \r\n         <div class=\"necqa_faqContact__panelInner\"> \r\n          <div class=\"necqa_faqContact__answerRow\"> \r\n           <span class=\"necqa_faqContact__aMark\" aria-hidden=\"true\">A</span> \r\n           <div class=\"necqa_faqContact__answer\"> \r\n            <p>お問い合わせ内容により窓口が異なります。</p> \r\n            <ul class=\"necqa_faqContact__answerList\"> \r\n             <li>購入前（製品選び・購入手続き）：FAQ／チャット</li> \r\n             <li>注文後（納期・注文内容・領収証など）：マイページ</li> \r\n             <li>購入後（使い方・故障・トラブル）：サポートサイト（購入後のお問い合わせ）</li> \r\n            </ul> \r\n           </div> \r\n          </div> \r\n         </div> \r\n        </div> \r\n       </details> </li> \r\n      <li class=\"necqa_faqContact__item\"> \r\n       <details class=\"necqa_faqContact__details\"> \r\n        <summary class=\"necqa_faqContact__summary\"> <span class=\"necqa_faqContact__summaryInner\"> <span class=\"necqa_faqContact__qMark\" aria-hidden=\"true\">Q</span> <span class=\"necqa_faqContact__question\"> 古いページに電話番号が載っています（電話してもよい？） </span> <span class=\"necqa_faqContact__toggle\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span> </span> </summary> \r\n        <div class=\"necqa_faqContact__panel\"> \r\n         <div class=\"necqa_faqContact__panelInner\"> \r\n          <div class=\"necqa_faqContact__answerRow\"> \r\n           <span class=\"necqa_faqContact__aMark\" aria-hidden=\"true\">A</span> \r\n           <div class=\"necqa_faqContact__answer\"> \r\n            <p> 一部の過去ページ・印刷物等に電話番号の記載が残っている場合があります。 最新の窓口は本FAQの案内に従ってください （NEC Directの購入前相談・注文関連は電話受付を行っておりません）。 </p> \r\n           </div> \r\n          </div> \r\n         </div> \r\n        </div> \r\n       </details> </li> \r\n      <li class=\"necqa_faqContact__item\"> \r\n       <details class=\"necqa_faqContact__details\"> \r\n        <summary class=\"necqa_faqContact__summary\"> <span class=\"necqa_faqContact__summaryInner\"> <span class=\"necqa_faqContact__qMark\" aria-hidden=\"true\">Q</span> <span class=\"necqa_faqContact__question\"> チャットの回答は電話で折り返しされますか？ </span> <span class=\"necqa_faqContact__toggle\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span> </span> </summary> \r\n        <div class=\"necqa_faqContact__panel\"> \r\n         <div class=\"necqa_faqContact__panelInner\"> \r\n          <div class=\"necqa_faqContact__answerRow\"> \r\n           <span class=\"necqa_faqContact__aMark\" aria-hidden=\"true\">A</span> \r\n           <div class=\"necqa_faqContact__answer\"> \r\n            <p> 原則として電話での折り返しは行いません。必要な場合は、チャット内またはメール等でご連絡します。 </p> \r\n           </div> \r\n          </div> \r\n         </div> \r\n        </div> \r\n       </details> </li> \r\n     </ul> \r\n    </div> \r\n   </section> \r\n   <section class=\"necqa_directCta\" aria-labelledby=\"necqa-directCta-title\"> \r\n    <div class=\"necqa_directCta__inner\"> \r\n     <h2 id=\"necqa-directCta-title\" class=\"necqa_directCta__title\"> お困りごとは、直接問い合わせでも解決できます！ </h2> \r\n     <ul class=\"necqa_directCta__list\"> \r\n      <li class=\"necqa_directCta__item\"> <a class=\"necqa_directCta__link necqa_directCta__link--inquiry\" href=\"/shop/info/guide/tel/\"> <span class=\"necqa_directCta__icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"> <img src=\"//p2-nec.static.pub/fes/cms/2026/03/30/hlyrpwqzfjoa72dysnf6q28yhewhtv063505.svg\" alt=\"\" width=\"56\" height=\"56\"> </span> <span class=\"necqa_directCta__text\">導入のご相談・<br class=\"u-only-sp\">お問い合わせ</span> </a> </li> \r\n      <li class=\"necqa_directCta__item\"> <a class=\"necqa_directCta__link necqa_directCta__link--chat\" href=\"/navigate/direct/info/chat/\"> <span class=\"necqa_directCta__icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"> <img src=\"//p4-nec.static.pub/fes/cms/2026/03/30/w5pxyh2071y219ra34vontgm4ipgkj370125.svg\" alt=\"\" width=\"81\" height=\"62\"> </span> <span class=\"necqa_directCta__text\">チャットで相談する</span> </a> </li> \r\n     </ul> \r\n    </div> \r\n   </section> \r\n   <section class=\"necqa_recommendBanners\" aria-labelledby=\"necqa-recommendBanners-title\"> \r\n    <div class=\"necqa_recommendBanners__inner\"> \r\n     <h2 id=\"necqa-recommendBanners-title\" class=\"necqa_recommendBanners__title\"> おすすめ情報 </h2> \r\n     <ul class=\"necqa_recommendBanners__list\"> \r\n      <li class=\"necqa_recommendBanners__item\"> <a class=\"necqa_recommendBanners__link\" href=\"/campaign/email/\"> <img class=\"necqa_recommendBanners__image necqa_recommendBanners__image--bleed\" src=\"https://p4-nec.static.pub/resource/NEC_Public_Resource/shop/mailmaga/images/page_bnr_mailmaga.webp\" alt=\"パソコン・タブレット メルマガ会員登録ですぐに特別優待価格で！ 詳細はこちら\" width=\"480\" height=\"160\"> </a> </li> \r\n      <li class=\"necqa_recommendBanners__item\"> <a class=\"necqa_recommendBanners__link\" href=\"/products/contents/\"> <img class=\"necqa_recommendBanners__image\" src=\"//p4-nec.static.pub/fes/cms/2026/03/30/8uqm948c2cbz1oga72ymxwsjdyucpa729717.png\" alt=\"特集記事 PCやタブレット等に関する各種お役立ち情報をお届けします。\" width=\"480\" height=\"160\"> </a> </li> \r\n     </ul> \r\n    </div> \r\n   </section> \r\n   <section class=\"necqa_supportLinks\" aria-labelledby=\"necqa-supportLinks-title\"> \r\n    <div class=\"necqa_supportLinks__inner\"> \r\n     <h2 id=\"necqa-supportLinks-title\" class=\"necqa_supportLinks__title\"> サポート関連リンク </h2> \r\n     <ul class=\"necqa_supportLinks__list\"> \r\n      <li class=\"necqa_supportLinks__item\"> <a class=\"necqa_supportLinks__link\" href=\"/shop/info/guide/inquiry/\"> ご購入相談・サポート </a> </li> \r\n      <li class=\"necqa_supportLinks__item\"> <a class=\"necqa_supportLinks__link\" href=\"/shop/info/guide/\"> ご利用ガイド </a> </li> \r\n     </ul> \r\n    </div> \r\n   </section> \r\n  </div> \r\n  <!-- // コンテンツここまで --> \r\n \r\n\r\n<script>\r\n    $(function () {\r\n        var storeData = nec_fe_core_tool.store.getStoreData();\r\n        if (storeData) {\r\n            nec_fe_core_tool.store.replaceRelativePath($(\"div[id='7a78a0a5-1292-467e-bf61-7836e82147aa']\"))\r\n        }\r\n    })\r\n</script>\r\n<div class=\"floatLayerClass\">     </div></div></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\t<div  width=\"100%2525\" height=\"100%\" level=\"1\" compId=\"3a9f1bb2-7f5d-4f84-94df-80d37d822cda\"  layoutId='3a9f1bb2-7f5d-4f84-94df-80d37d822cda' id=\"ef7c5023-0925-4330-8b08-04887bdb30bc\" order=\"2\"    cssPath='' jsPath=''\r\nclass=\"container9999 clearfix cms_layoutBox_auto_height cms_background_layout_color_ef7c5023-0925-4330-8b08-04887bdb30bc cms_background_layout_img_type0_ef7c5023-0925-4330-8b08-04887bdb30bc\" style=\"display: -webkit-box;width:100%;\">\r\n<style>\r\n    .cms_currency_layout{\r\n        border: 0px solid;\r\n        border-color: red;\r\n        margin:0 auto;\r\n        posi